41) Analyze website traffic patterns for reporting
Implementation: GA4 + data warehouse; generate insights weekly.
Best AI: GPT-4; BI tool NLQ; Jasper for marketing-ready summaries.[^5][^8][^12]
42) Process survey responses for trend analysis
Implementation: Thematic clustering; verbatim quotes; dashboards.
Best AI: Claude 3.5; GPT-4; BI tools with text analytics.[^13][^12]
43) Generate KPI dashboards from multiple data sources
Implementation: Federated connectors; KPI contracts; alerting.
Best AI: Power BI + Copilot; Jaspersoft for embedded use cases.[^3][^12][^5]
44) Extract project milestones from task management tools
Implementation: API integration; milestone logic; weekly digest.
Best AI: Claude 3.5; Copilot; Monday AI.[^20][^30]
45) Analyze call center data for performance metrics
Implementation: Speech analytics; handle time/CSAT; agent coaching.
Best AI: Copilot + Teams; GPT-4; vendor CCaaS AI.[^33][^34][^4]

